    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继承祖母的餐厅，打造繁荣的餐馆，目标——三颗星餐厅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入童话世界，和敌人战斗并收集食材，享受精彩的动作体验，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时还可以雇佣和培养员工，经营你的餐厅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款结合<strong>餐厅经营</strong>与<strong>童话动作</strong>的游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>　　　　</u></strong><u>童话动作<strong>　　　　</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集食材</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入童话世界，收集各种各样的食材吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打败生物，有时还能获得珍贵的食材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集得越多，餐厅能提供的美食也越丰富！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/c88aab31b36e49589568ea2af1af7304.poster.avif?t=1765013325\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/c88aab31b36e49589568ea2af1af7304.webm?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/c88aab31b36e49589568ea2af1af7304.mp4?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>童话技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中可借助童话角色的力量，施展强大的童话技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活运用，让战斗更加轻松！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/e9801bbe77991e2b59fa4df72ca0891e.poster.avif?t=1765013325\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/e9801bbe77991e2b59fa4df72ca0891e.webm?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/e9801bbe77991e2b59fa4df72ca0891e.mp4?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>料理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用收集到的食材，制作美味料理吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物可以恢复HP、让敌人陷入异常状态，还有更多妙用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以不断收集食材，也可以用料理增强自己，挑战强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/f9a29dcc3ecc2adee0feaa6edfd19187.avif?t=1765013325\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras_big/f9a29dcc3ecc2adee0feaa6edfd19187.avif?t=1765013325 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>　　　　餐厅经营　　　　</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>员工</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以雇佣员工来经营餐厅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理安排他们在擅长的岗位上，让餐厅运转更加高效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/6b190362305bf558590c7b6860cf4b51.avif?t=1765013325\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras_big/6b190362305bf558590c7b6860cf4b51.avif?t=1765013325 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>营业中</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >营业时会发生各种事件！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招揽顾客</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清扫店内</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上菜服务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赶走捣乱的客人</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妥善应对，让顾客满意吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/2f1e717d83b2a25b3d35892082d620c0.poster.avif?t=1765013325\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/2f1e717d83b2a25b3d35892082d620c0.webm?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173430/extras/2f1e717d83b2a25b3d35892082d620c0.mp4?t=1765013325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u> 　　　　</u></strong><u>其他要素<strong>　　　　 </strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中食用料理，永久强化角色能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过挑战解锁新关卡和食谱！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u> 　　　直播指南　　　 </u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是个人还是公司，都可以在没有事先许可的情况下上传和直播视频。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于盈利化和游戏范围也没有任何限制。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br><i>Powered by “CRIWARE”.CRIWARE is a trademark of CRI Middleware Co., Ltd.</i></p>",
